channel.title: If someone gives me their skill .txt would it work for me?
channel.description: I was wondering if i take someones fletching/smelting/crafting .txts and paste em on my source, would it work for me? I really need this because my source DC's you when you ATTEMPT to do any of the above skills. Or can I fix this?

item.title: If someone gives me their skill .txt would it work for me?
item.dc:creator: @DannyIsSoPro DannyIsSoPro
item.description:
@DannyIsSoPro wrote:

[quote=“ston3, post:8, topic:441559”][quote author=sk8rdude461 link=topic=544257.msg3989390#msg3989390 date=1336351556]
Am I the only one here that’s confused… He’s asking for a text file. Servers use java…
So where ever this error is coming from, it isn’t your text files…
[/quote]Typo .java lol[/quote]

Copy-pasting those skill classes won’t work because the class will have different imports from your server. Just write them yourself; you will learn if you mess with things.
